import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---
<Layout title="Technical Details - Insight Hunter">
  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Technical Specifications of Insight Hunter</p>
    <p>Insight Hunter is built on a modern tech stack emphasising security, performance, and scalability. The core platform uses Astro for the frontend, with SCSS for styling and components for modularity. Backend integrations include secure API connections for bank data (read-only) and AI processing via natural language models.</p>
    <p>Key technologies: Python for data processing (with libraries like pandas and numpy), AI frameworks for query handling, and cloud services for Enterprise editions. All editions support cross-platform use, with local-first options in Lite to ensure data privacy. Compliance features adhere to GAAP standards, with encryption for all transmissions.</p>
    <p>For company updates on technical advancements, check the updates page. News on industry tech trends is available in the news section. Contact us for custom technical consultations or refer to FAQs for common tech queries.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
